  "detailed_description": "In this puzzle game you control a plane and draw figures with a smoke trail.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTo progress you have to be precise, but to excel you also need to be fast and smart.<br />\r\nThere are 60 levels, can you get three stars on all of them?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPop the balloons for bonus credits and to increase your score.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn free form creative mode your imagination is the only limit.<br />\r\nDraw whatever you want!<br />\r\nUse various smoke trails to make even more crazy drawings!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUnlock new planes and paintjobs to customize them!",
  "about_the_game": "In this puzzle game you control a plane and draw figures with a smoke trail.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTo progress you have to be precise, but to excel you also need to be fast and smart.<br />\r\nThere are 60 levels, can you get three stars on all of them?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPop the balloons for bonus credits and to increase your score.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn free form creative mode your imagination is the only limit.<br />\r\nDraw whatever you want!<br />\r\nUse various smoke trails to make even more crazy drawings!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUnlock new planes and paintjobs to customize them!",
